# 🛡️ SOC Analyst Career Roadmap

A Security Operations Center (SOC) Analyst is the first line of defense against cyber threats. SOC Analysts monitor security events, investigate suspicious activities, analyze logs, detect attacks, respond to incidents, and help protect an organization's infrastructure through continuous monitoring and threat detection.

