# 🏆 Capstone Projects

1. Build a Complete Home SOC Lab (Windows + Linux + Sysmon + Wazuh + Splunk).
2. Investigate a Simulated Ransomware Attack from Initial Alert to Final Incident Report.
3. Create a Threat Detection Rule Pack using Sigma, Splunk SPL, Microsoft Sentinel KQL, and Elastic.
4. Design an Enterprise SOC Architecture with SIEM, SOAR, Threat Intelligence, and Detection Pipelines.
5. Perform a Complete Threat Hunt using PCAPs, Windows Event Logs, Sysmon Logs, and MITRE ATT&CK Mapping.
